r\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Email: rafat.qayum_ne@ntucguest.com\\\",\\\"status\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"Done\\\",\\\"category\\\":\\\"Done\\\"},\\\"assignee\\\":\\\"Michael Bui\\\",\\\"priority\\\":\\\"High\\\",\\\"labels\\\":[\\\"priority:operations\\\"],\\\"duedate\\\":null,\\\"parent\\\":null,\\\"subtasks\\\":[],\\\"links\\\":[],\\\"created\\\":\\\"2026-01-15T13:23:57.522+0800\\\",\\\"updated\\\":\\\"2026-01-19T15:50:53.784+0800\\\",\\\"comments\\\":[{\\\"created\\\":\\\"2026-01-15T14:03:14.614+0800\\\",\\\"updated\\\":\\\"2026-01-15T14:03:14.614+0800\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"Michael Bui\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"IT Helpdesk ticket is created:\\\"},{\\\"created\\\":\\\"2026-01-15T13:51:20.024+0800\\\",\\\"updated\\\":\\\"2026-01-15T13:51:20.024+0800\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"Michael Bui\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"Approved by :\\\"}]},{\\\"key\\\":\\\"OMNI-1297\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"502092\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Near Real-time Inventory Indexing for FFS to Decrease OOS Impressions on Search\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Problem Definition\\\\nWhat problem/opportunity do the customers face that you are trying to solve?\\\\nCustomers frequently encounter discrepancies in product availability and information. A common complaint is that products shown as “out of stock” online are actually available in-store. Similarly, incorrect or outdated product tagging (e.g. dietary info, price, secondary category) impacts browsing, sorting, and personalization quality.\\\\nThis affects:\\\\nCustomer trust in stock and pricing information\\\\n\\\\nSearch and discovery relevance, especially during campaigns\\\\n\\\\nOperational productivity of the Backoffice (DBP) and Tech teams, due to frequent manual overrides and support tickets\\\\n\\\\nRevenue opportunities, particularly during high-traffic events like CNY or Xmas\\\\n\\\\n\\\\nAs a FairPrice app/web user,\\\\nWhen I browse or search for products\\\\nI want to see up-to-date stock levels, prices, and tags\\\\nSo I can confidently choose and purchase available items\\\\n🧑‍🤝‍🧑 Who Faces This Problem and Its Importance\\\\nAffected Users:\\\\nOnline and in-store customers using the app or website for search/browsing\\\\n\\\\nDBP (Backoffice) operators who update product metadata\\\\n\\\\nTech team supporting urgent data fix tickets\\\\n\\\\n\\\\nDuring CNY\\\\n% Impression on OOS\\\\npage_type\\\\n\\\\nweek\\\\ncategory\\\\nsearch\\\\n1\\\\n2.18%\\\\n2.97%\\\\n2\\\\n2.84%\\\\n3.36%\\\\n3\\\\n2.66%\\\\n3.18%\\\\n4\\\\n3.32%\\\\n3.56%\\\\n5\\\\n6.18%\\\\n8.85%\\\\n6\\\\n4.06%\\\\n4.79%\\\\n7\\\\n2.92%\\\\n3.40%\\\\nEstimated Impact:\\\\nGMV impact of $1.72M\\\\n\\\\nImprove customer experience NPS\\\\n\\\\n\\\\nImportance:\\\\nHigh — impacts trust, conversion, cart additions, and operational efficiency\\\\n\\\\nRelevance and freshness of content is core to any modern retail platform\\\\n\\\\n\\\\nCurrent Workarounds:\\\\nManual fixes via Backoffice\\\\n\\\\nAd hoc alerts and re-indexing requests\\\\n\\\\nFull-table scans every 1 hours, incurring cost and latency\\\\n\\\\n\\\\nSuccess Criteria\\\",\\\"status\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"Backlog\\\",\\\"category\\\":\\\"To Do\\\"},\\\"assignee\\\":\\\"Prajney Sribhashyam\\\",\\\"priority\\\":\\\"High\\\",\\\"labels\\\":[],\\\"duedate\\\":null,\\\"parent\\\":null,\\\"subtasks\\\":[],\\\"links\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Polaris work item link\\\",\\\"key\\\":\\\"PRDM-239\\\"}],\\\"created\\\":\\\"2025-06-10T11:07:28.181+0800\\\",\\\"updated\\\":\\\"2026-01-19T11:46:36.520+0800\\\",\\\"comments\\\":[{\\\"created\\\":\\\"2026-01-19T11:46:36.520+0800\\\",\\\"updated\\\":\\\"2026-01-19T11:46:36.520+0800\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"Prajney Sribhashyam\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"To be covered in re-platform\\\"},{\\\"created\\\":\\\"2025-10-28T22:32:33.016+0800\\\",\\\"updated\\\":\\\"2025-10-28T22:32:33.016+0800\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"Prajney Sribhashyam\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"Available to promise - Estimated annual GMV impact $1M-$1.25M vs Effort estimate - Small\\\\nNear real time inventory - Estimated annual GMV impact ~$1.5M vs Effort estimate - Medium to large\\\\n\\\\nCan deprioritise from pre-holiday must have list\\\"},{\\\"created\\\":\\\"2025-10-22T10:24:43.121+0800\\\",\\\"updated\\\":\\\"2025-10-28T21:50:36.932+0800\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"Prajney Sribhashyam\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"Pending discussion during pitch session. If deprioritised, the Available to Promise initiative will replace NRTI in priorities.\\\"},{\\\"created\\\":\\\"2025-10-17T12:15:49.246+0800\\\",\\\"updated\\\":\\\"2025-10-17T12:17:30.247+0800\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"Ryne Cheow\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"As shared over chat, the solution would be able to reuse for replatform and it is still a medium effort as shared in the previous weeks. \\\\n\\\\n as of now till an overriding decision happens (supposedly 21st October 2025) - this is deprioritised still according to this \\\\n\\\\ncc\\\"},{\\\"created\\\":\\\"2025-10-16T11:03:02.728+0800\\\",\\\"updated\\\":\\\"2025-10-16T11:03:02.728+0800\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"Prajney Sribhashyam\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"Next steps\\\\n   to assist the group in evaluating Near Real Time Inventory vs Available to Promise\\\\n\\\\n1.  to come back with approach for NRTI\\\\n2.  to put together a pitch for ‘Available to Promise’ with help from  \\\\n3. Re-group on 21 Oct 2025 to take a decision\\\"},{\\\"created\\\":\\\"2025-10-16T10:42:21.080+0800\\\",\\\"updated\\\":\\\"2025-10-16T10:42:21.080+0800\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"Qiuyan Tian\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"to come back with solution, so that we can decide.\\\"},{\\\"created\\\":\\\"2025-10-15T10:40:13.908+0800\\\",\\\"updated\\\":\\\"2025-10-15T10:40:13.908+0800\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"Prajney Sribhashyam\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"Solution alignment pending. Target date: 17 Oct\\\\nNeed to start development right away if we are to deliver this before freeze. Hence the target date.\\\"},{\\\"created\\\":\\\"2025-10-14T10:44:34.303+0800\\\",\\\"updated\\\":\\\"2025-10-14T10:49:21.935+0800\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"Prajney Sribhashyam\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"confirmed with  \\\\nT-shirt size M. Solution might not survive re-platform. Need to prioritise accordingly.\\\\nFeedback from engg: If we need it before CNY, needs to be picked up immediately.\\\"},{\\\"created\\\":\\\"2025-10-14T10:41:03.206+0800\\\",\\\"updated\\\":\\\"2025-10-14T10:41:03.206+0800\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"Prajney Sribhashyam\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"Could you please help with the following information:\\\\nT-shirt size for the initiative\\\\n\\\\nWill the solution survive beyond re-platform?\\\"},{\\\"created\\\":\\\"2025-10-14T10:34:44.585+0800\\\",\\\"updated\\\":\\\"2025-10-14T10:36:32.331+0800\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"Prajney Sribhashyam\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"If ROI is low, we can skip this initiative, based on Sean’s feedback\\\\n\\\\nAction items:\\\\n1. Get t-shirt size for the initiative  (ETA 16 Oct 2025)\\\\n2. Re-evaluate ROI & prioritise accordingly\\\"}]},{\\\"key\\\":\\\"RM-697\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"574486\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Web - OG Home - Testhas Offer swimlane - Ad label is missing for the first listed product\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Login to the application withj Valid creds.\\\\n\\\\nMake sure the postal code is set to 098619\\\\n\\\\nScroll down on Home page until Testhas Offer swimlane is displayed.\\\\n\\\\n\\\\nActual Result - Verify that the first listed product is not showing the Ad label.\\\\nExpected Result - Show Ad in the first of the product under the Testhas Offer swimlane.\\\\nIssue is only with Web. It is good in iOS and Android\\\\nhttps://app.testsigma.com/ui/td/test_case_results/16571301/step_results\\\",\\\"status\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"To Do\\\",\\\"category\\\":\\\"To Do\\\"},\\\"assignee\\\":\\\"Michael Bui\\\",\\\"priority\\\":\\\"High\\\",\\\"labels\\\":[\\\"found-in-e2e-automation\\\",\\\"priority:health\\\"],\\\"duedate\\\":null,\\\"parent\\\":null,\\\"subtasks\\\":[],\\\"links\\\":[],\\\"created\\\":\\\"2026-01-05T15:13:22.435+0800\\\",\\\"updated\\\":\\\"2026-01-14T15:28